{"tid":433532,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界大戰] FF機選擇  NIKON VS SONY","createTime":"2017-10-12T12:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T15:33:46.000Z","uid":12302,"like":14,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e4217698ad5d1383ccf7cb1f4173e7008deacdec","tid":433532,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"主影景 副影人 街拍<br />\n<br />\n暫時想出D810 / A7RII <br />\n<br />\nBUDGET: ~35K 連一枝ULTRA WIDE, 一枝TELE 可以既話一枝平既PRIME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D810<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> A7RII<br />\n<br />\n其他歡迎留言<br />\n含撚貓可以出番去"},{"pid":"a5db3ab34dc50c03cce509d7b16b83f4f6917cdc","tid":433532,"uid":77298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"Sony a7rii a9 用家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔d850? Out budget??"},{"pid":"c8fa85373a8c0081b016fb22d2f187afd942d8c7","tid":433532,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sony a7rii a9 用家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔d850? Out budget??</blockquote><br />\n太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7bb14dbdc78189e7dbf54fd93e1815395c4264","tid":433532,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"A7RII"},{"pid":"7877553653246a1a207f772319205585d874cb87","tid":433532,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"Canon 6D Mark II"},{"pid":"9a3ef22f039b972b88f042fb28af3b8f21752a16","tid":433532,"uid":77298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sony a7rii a9 用家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔d850? Out budget??</blockquote><br />\n太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重量係你嘅重要考慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影景同街拍<br />\n揀鏡都要小心<br />\n揀錯你會無心機出動"},{"pid":"eec3a6c40e28496c19a7c811b0a5fbf6452d5d68","tid":433532,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"sony係打算邊3支鏡？？？"},{"pid":"4e13ee81ecda0ae002ef2f94bc586f4c9eb6f691","tid":433532,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sony係打算邊3支鏡？？？</blockquote><br />\nGm 大三元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4149704822b39fc00c776da01505c8bff6cec5a","tid":433532,"uid":77298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Sony a7rii a9 用家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔d850? Out budget??</blockquote><br />\n太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重量係你嘅重要考慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影景同街拍<br />\n揀鏡都要小心<br />\n揀錯你會無心機出動</blockquote><br />\nA7rii + 12-24 f4 + 70-200 f4<br />\n有錢先再諗 55 1.8 or 85 1.8"},{"pid":"f3b1a1c1509f54f1e248ea644aa211155e140f10","tid":433532,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"各位可唔可以比埋原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ed93978baea91fabf362e7a8452a28fc3617da","tid":433532,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>sony係打算邊3支鏡？？？</blockquote><br />\nGm 大三元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n配返呢3支咪又重到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e935cda2fdcb7b9bd268661b7524a0c6c46af7c","tid":433532,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"a7r2 $164xx + <br />\n1635z $8260 + <br />\nMetabones 5 $3000 + Canon 70-200 f4 non is 水貨 $3,800 +<br />\nsamyang af 35mm f2.8 $2500<br />\n<br />\n1635z 評價唔錯，假如你覺得16唔夠wide 就轉sony 1224 <br />\n1224 加3千  應該爆少少畢直<br />\n點解係mb5 + canon 70－200 f4 non is <br />\n係因為 有左mb5 第日入其他canon 鏡會更方便，<br />\n而sony 70－200 f4 要成8千，咁樣入仲平過sony 原廠。<br />\n點解揀non is 係因為本身已經有五軸防震，<br />\n加上你話影風景多，所以我諗鏡頭 is 對你黎講，相對無咁重要。<br />\na7r2 加 mb5 既對焦速度絕對可用，我見你無寫影運動先咁推，如果你要影運動就接返原廠。<br />\n買水貨係因為平1000蚊 支鏡本身就唔係話好貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  介意就買返行貨<br />\n淨返少少錢 三陽35mm f2.8 又平又輕，方便日常使用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：新手鳩up"},{"pid":"43688a4b301720d3aae12429ae5827682054886a","tid":433532,"uid":13796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:27:58.000Z","msg":"我就係由D700轉去A7ii既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSony <br />\n好：二千萬crop 相夠方便，機細，方便，公廁乜鏡都插得，玩舊鏡有peaking 對焦冇煩惱<br />\n<br />\n壞：食電，好撚食電，我D700一粒電可以玩足一晚慢快門影星，而家長期兩粒至少...更加唔好諗夜晚玩Time Lapse(但A7iiR 可以長插奶媽冇煩惱）<br />\n<br />\n光學Viewfinder VS 電子 Viewfinder <br />\n<br />\n頭重尾輕，就算部機點細點輕，鏡頭大細都改唔到，變相唔會細得幾多<br />\n<br />\n味精Mon, 影完係部機睇同係電腦睇係唔同色。<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n我D700轉就無懸念，D700像數低，用CF。已經夠理由換機。加上我上年托住部D700+24-70/2.8 去冰島行冰川好撚痛苦，所以決心換機。<br />\n<br />\n而家日常出街玩就A7ii加轉插隊Nikon 35mm, 大細重量都可以接受，若果影星星就14-24/2.8 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/212704_3f907e35df1314de0c999ec41aff2854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F212704_3f907e35df1314de0c999ec41aff2854.jpg&h=ec8d855a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送一張係New Zealand 既星星。 A7ii + 14-24/2.8"},{"pid":"1db052cac6742beb2007e746b23ee50c4aee1351","tid":433532,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a341e21f8bbb5f376fd4c5da971c07bd80e6ec6","tid":433532,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"1424 都麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cdd566768fc7eb4ea0f344c65c86621d4866f9","tid":433532,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec3c0d31051a962e506156b977419ae2034db07","tid":433532,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13f03cc65b7b5fb5dfaa51f079ba450944f09f38","tid":433532,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"唔係話10/18sony有新機發佈會咩，不如等多幾日先講啦"},{"pid":"9cb02ab5c322c2a6dcc5958ea77fa3a8d71785ac","tid":433532,"uid":69221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1424 都麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/214750_138a31825460ad29e8e056b08757db88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F214750_138a31825460ad29e8e056b08757db88.jpg&h=fe8fd8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔知呢支咩鏡啦<br />\n<br />\n不過邊緣個屎忽夠曬結實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a1df2b2475cdf0ae14a32908ded0d72536ee06","tid":433532,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61d8ee210a03dd55f3582881e777338e2175aaa7","tid":433532,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"sony 啲鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0daee49851ee66f00ecd5be055766d0a1b9c96e","tid":433532,"uid":104387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1424 都麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/214750_138a31825460ad29e8e056b08757db88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F214750_138a31825460ad29e8e056b08757db88.jpg&h=fe8fd8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔知呢支咩鏡啦<br />\n<br />\n不過邊緣個屎忽夠曬結實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無聊</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aY097.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aY097.gif&h=cd5219bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e39f34032c8c17c7824c1daea793655482070a3a","tid":433532,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"d810 iso 表現真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申用緊。"},{"pid":"1e1ce650d218d9b26c4f632f73a927f45824a014","tid":433532,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1424 都麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公道講  真係冇點處理過彗星像差<br />\n<br />\n不過zoom lens計冇唔係問題既 否則應該貴到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但budget問題所以唔處理過彗星像差=/=冇改善地方既"},{"pid":"51c3f448b0b61a90c42e9076840bd930954f5b84","tid":433532,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1424 都麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公道講  真係冇點處理過彗星像差<br />\n<br />\n不過zoom lens計冇唔係問題既 否則應該貴到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">budget問題</span>所以唔處理過彗星像差=/=冇改善地方既</blockquote><br />\n唔係話Sony冇錢  係話支鏡唔可以賣得太貴"},{"pid":"f43556ce9ba615c4b76c1ec2d4dc542c7b3b0313","tid":433532,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a7r2 $164xx + <br />\n1635z $8260 + <br />\nMetabones 5 $3000 + Canon 70-200 f4 non is 水貨 $3,800 +<br />\nsamyang af 35mm f2.8 $2500<br />\n<br />\n1635z 評價唔錯，假如你覺得16唔夠wide 就轉sony 1224 <br />\n1224 加3千  應該爆少少畢直<br />\n點解係mb5 + canon 70－200 f4 non is <br />\n係因為 有左mb5 第日入其他canon 鏡會更方便，<br />\n而sony 70－200 f4 要成8千，咁樣入仲平過sony 原廠。<br />\n點解揀non is 係因為本身已經有五軸防震，<br />\n加上你話影風景多，所以我諗鏡頭 is 對你黎講，相對無咁重要。<br />\na7r2 加 mb5 既對焦速度絕對可用，我見你無寫影運動先咁推，如果你要影運動就接返原廠。<br />\n買水貨係因為平1000蚊 支鏡本身就唔係話好貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  介意就買返行貨<br />\n淨返少少錢 三陽35mm f2.8 又平又輕，方便日常使用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：新手鳩up</blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得70200 sony原廠好啲喎，f4都係9000蚊到，mb5+小小白都7000幾蚊<br />\n如果唔用canon原廠鏡的話，mc11都唔錯，平一半又可以插到sigma art鏡<br />\nbtw，如果想要70200 2.8嘅話， 龍仔G2唔錯，睇你有冇需要<br />\n當然...買得mc11嘅可以考慮全部鏡頭都唔係sony鏡嘅...睇你肯唔肯"},{"pid":"b7802c4b5e8b89f87faeacbfb527af220f636b97","tid":433532,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:15:07.000Z","msg":"如果係咁 加多個條件 會影銀河影星<br />\nsony wide/ultra wide有咩選擇<br />\nf4怕且唔太夠用"},{"pid":"048dfbb1f8f4fb7d0a900898bd5ab9fcdbdeb749","tid":433532,"uid":1748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T20:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係咁 加多個條件 會影銀河影星<br />\nsony wide/ultra wide有咩選擇<br />\nf4怕且唔太夠用</blockquote><br />\n老蛙手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc236d85632722de92b97bff1f90e8da9952a31a","tid":433532,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係咁 加多個條件 會影銀河影星<br />\nsony wide/ultra wide有咩選擇<br />\nf4怕且唔太夠用</blockquote><br />\n老蛙手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哩個應該無咩異議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係sigma 14 Art"},{"pid":"86c16ad726ea54ca865a96bdee5f13d398cb32ca","tid":433532,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"810唔建議，ISO衰過750<br />\nA7IIR唔可以粗用，基本上SONY機仲脆弱過BB仔或者你部手機<br />\n你忍到就用啦，BESTCHOICE"},{"pid":"14b0249be40ce64873c044b4f0b2d1d9f60c7100","tid":433532,"uid":799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"2部都用過,比較之下:<br />\n<br />\n略略講下兩邊既優/缺<br />\nd810優:<br />\n- 低iso 好細緻 iso 64 比起索尼果個iso 50 仲好d<br />\n- dynamic range 高d, 執相果時發覺<br />\n- 電量幾好<br />\n缺:<br />\n- 重<br />\n- 低光對焦=垃圾<br />\n<br />\na7r2優:<br />\n- 輕<br />\n- 萬能插<br />\n- 低光對焦都唔差<br />\n<br />\n缺:<br />\n- 色柒<br />\n- buffer 耐, 呢個真係好戇鳩"},{"pid":"beb1f80ac7e3e5d55506591fff04a5ffa4368acd","tid":433532,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2部都用過,比較之下:<br />\n<br />\n略略講下兩邊既優/缺<br />\nd810優:<br />\n- 低iso 好細緻 iso 64 比起索尼果個iso 50 仲好d<br />\n- dynamic range 高d, 執相果時發覺<br />\n- 電量幾好<br />\n缺:<br />\n- 重<br />\n- 低光對焦=垃圾<br />\n<br />\na7r2優:<br />\n- 輕<br />\n- 萬能插<br />\n- 低光對焦都唔差<br />\n<br />\n缺:<br />\n- 色柒<br />\n- buffer 耐, 呢個真係好戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有d810 高iso表現 比a7r2屌打"},{"pid":"707023c9199d00abd1d02a6cd56965b53a54ae61","tid":433532,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T12:04:07.000Z","m